{% set version = "0.9" %}

package:
  name: py-graphviz
  version: '{{ version }}'

source:
  url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/g/graphviz/graphviz-{{ version }}.zip
  sha256: '{{ sha256 }}'

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv .

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - graphviz
